cheetah :"we dont' even know where we are"
 Nic <wingedwarrior41@...> wrote:Tyrael: Meet back at Blackheart's ship.

--- In nbwrpg@y..., Tankor <lordofdarkness11001@y...> wrote:
> 
> Cheetah: "tyrael wher are you. tigerhawk and i got out just in time
>  Nic <wingedwarrior41@h...> wrote:In the sky, the Tripredacus ship 
exploded. The explosions started to 
> blow up the engines first, then expanded to the rest of the ship. It 
> did not even have time to crash as it came apart in the air. Burning 
> pieces of metal and smoldering airborne ruins fell down hard.
> 
> Tyrael looked around. His ship and his command were gone, unless 
> Cheetah and Tigerhawk had managed to get out. He was decided to end 
> the battle though. He looked for Rodimus.
> 
> Tyrael: Rodimus, Tyrael here. Mind keeping a piece of Hydras for me?
> 
> Sanguine and Meteara were in heavy combat. Sanguine rushed at the 
Vok 
> and threw her in the air. Meteara quickly engaged her jets to get 
> control, but was hit by a fiery steel beam. She was grounded but 
came 
> back.
> 
> Sanguine approached her with deadly determination. She made a fierce 
> looking stiletto out of her hand brought it closer and closer to her 
> enemy's head.
> 
> Meteara: Why do you want to kill me?
> 
> Sanguine breathed heavily. Why? There was too much to be said.
> 
> Sanguine: Your race killed a brethren of mine. There is something in 
> Predacon behavior that is called vengeance. That is what's going on.
> 
> Little did she notice the crackling sound growing louder and louder. 
> As the tip of her weapon was in range of the Vok, a massive electric 
> jolt jumped on it and shocked the criminal. She fell hard to the 
> ground too. Meteara stood up. She was clearly wounded too.
> 
> Meteara: I too have many assets. Let's finish this folly.
> 
> Sanguine: Yes, you are right.
> 
> In an instant, Meteara started firing innumerable bullets from her 
> machine guns. At the same moment, Sanguine morphed. She made a 
beast's 
> head out of her legs and went at Meteara...
>
